      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GOT THIS GIRLS (2) was a last start winner (25.05) at this track who is building a strong winning record. Strike rate this distance strong having won four of six tries. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Makes plenty of appeal if runs up to latest. CANYA ROMANCE (6) is a super honest type rarely out of the placings, including wins at her last three on end, the latest at this track (25.27). Goes very well here at the trip finding the frame in each of six starts. Looks well placed here and has the ability. Go well. MR. LASSO (3) boasts strong form at this course and distance having won six times from seven starts. Scored by 4.5 lengths last time (25.36) in a Grade 5 over 457m at this track. Looks suited here and can measure up. SPECIAL ROCKY (1) picked up a cheque over this course and distance most recently - in the mix again.",
